    LinoriaLib v2 — Enhanced Edition
    Improvements over v1:
      • Full mobile/touch support (Touch tap, pan, long-press)
      • Bug fixes (Tween.Clean self-ref, Connect thread overhead, OpenFrames leak)
      • No RenderStepped for popup positioning (AbsolutePosition signal + one-shot update)
      • Smooth spring-based open/close animations (Back easing on open, Quint on close)
      • ViewportFrame 3D character preview widget
      • Adaptive layout (scales hit-targets on mobile, GuiService inset aware)
      • UIScale auto-adjust for small screens
--]]

